title: Girl on a Chain Gang (1966 Crime) This Town Got Ways of Teaching You a Lesson!

sources.title: Girl on a Chain Gang (1966 Crime) This Town Got Ways of Teaching You a Lesson!
sources.description:
When Diane (Julie Ange), Bill (William Watson), and Paul (Ron Charles) are wrongfully locked up in a corrupt Southern jail, they must outwit their captors and break free from the chains that bind them. Racing against time and tyranny, this daring trio turns the tables in a high-stakes game of justice and escape.


Colorized version: https://youtu.be/rCcz7qdIZPA

Director: Jerry Gross
Writers: Jerry Gross, Don Olsen
Actors: William Watson, Julie Ange, Ron Charles
